title: Cacai Bautista trends with rendition of ‘Bakit Nga Ba Mahal Kita?’
text: By: Clarizel Abanilla - Entertainment Correspondent / @CAbanillaINQ INQUIRER.net / 07:58 PM February 23, 2017 Image: Screen grab from Cacai Bautista’s “Wishclusive” performance Comedian-singer Cacai Bautista trends yet again for her sentimental rendition of the classic Roselle Nava song “Bakit Nga Ba Mahal Kita?” Bautista made the performance during her guesting on Wish 107.5. Her number garnered thousands of views since its release on Wednesday (February 22). Just like her previous “Wishclusive” performances, Bautista gained praises from netizens for her powerful take on the 90’s classic.
